Title: Replication Slaves should lock WATO
Component: wato
State: open
Date: 2011-12-08 16:50:35
Targetversion: 1.2.0
Class: todo

A replication Slave should lock WATO. This feature could be 
configured in the Replication configuration in WATO. We
could set the lock while the master is logged in in the slave.
